Ranger Help for: prospect
=========================

SYNTAX:      prospect
USAGE:       Mountain/hills only
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to search the surrounding area for mineral
deposits such as gold, silver, and other ores. Prospecting can only be
done in mountain or hills terrain. A successful prospect reveals whether
the area contains mineable deposits and what type of minerals are
present. This information is used in conjunction with the mine skill
to extract ore nuggets for crafting arrow tips and other items.
